#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2026-05-12-quarkus-insights-247-agentic-orchestration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Journey: From Spring Boot to Quarkus"
msgstr "El viaje: De Spring Boot a Quarkus"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-12-quarkus-insights-247-agentic-orchestration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Jonathan's journey began with a home lab project using Spring Boot and Spring AI. After attending a Connecticut Java Users Group talk by Eric Deandrea (from the Quarkus team), he was inspired to explore LangChain4j with Quarkus. Using https://claude.ai/[Claude AI] for code conversion, he successfully migrated his Spring Boot application to Quarkus with LangChain4j in approximately one hour."
msgstr "El viaje de Jonathan comenzó con un proyecto de laboratorio casero utilizando Spring Boot y Spring AI. Tras asistir a una charla del Connecticut Java Users Group a cargo de Eric Deandrea (del equipo de Quarkus), se inspiró para explorar LangChain4j con Quarkus. Utilizando link:https://claude.ai/[Claude AI] para la conversión de código, migró con éxito su aplicación Spring Boot a Quarkus con LangChain4j en aproximadamente una hora."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-12-quarkus-insights-247-agentic-orchestration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Key migration benefits observed:\n"
"- Faster startup times\n"
"- Reduced memory footprint\n"
"- Lower CPU usage\n"
"- Native compilation with https://www.graalvm.org/[GraalVM] support"
msgstr "Beneficios clave de la migración observados: - Tiempos de arranque más rápidos - Menor huella de memoria - Menor uso de la CPU - Compilación nativa compatible con link:https://www.graalvm.org/[GraalVM]"

